## Airtable Base Auto-Backup
A set of Apps and Automations backup the table data and files from an Airtable base to an independent server. 

##### Automated - at scheduled time
![Pasted image 20220508201944.png](data:image/png;base64,)
##### By Request
- **Backup tables** creates a **csv** file with all table data, including link data for lossless restoring of data links
- **Collect files** looks thru all datasets for attachment and collects them into a **zip** archive. 
	![Pasted image 20220508202345.png](data:image/png;base64,)
##### Backed-up Data File Storage
is stored at [[Public Website/Monito.website Data Hub|Monito.website Data Hub]]: a dedicated file server with multiple account accessn and direct download functionality
![Pasted image 20220508202549.png](data:image/png;base64,)
##### Restore from Backup
an app for restoring the backed up data into an Airtable base, rebuilding the links and uploading files
![Pasted image 20220508202958.png](data:image/png;base64,)
